high_descs: Take the bread out of the fridge.
Bring the bread to the microwave.
Heat the bread in the microwave.
Take the bread to the fridge.
Put the bread back in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Heat the bread, put it back in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around.  Move towards the door.  At the door turn left to face the fridge.
Grab the bread that is on the top shelf.
Turn left and move to the stove.
Open the microwave.  Put the bread in the microwave.  Turn the microwave on.  When finished take the bread out of the microwave.
Turn all the way around.  Move towards the door.  At the door turn left to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the bread on the top shelf to the left of the green jar.
anns.task_desc: Warm the bread up in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Take the bread out of the fridge.
Turn around and walk right to the microwave.
Heat the bread in the microwave.
Turn around and walk back to the fridge.
Put the bread on the top shelf of the fridge to the left of the green item.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated loaf of bread in a fridge.
